| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-2410 — Recovery Inhibition (thegentlemen)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: b379e80d-c236-53ea-8eb8-f5e6fc9a3522"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
